    question: "How do I know if my frames need restoration?",
    answer: "You may benefit from anodized frame restoration if your aluminum window or door frames show signs of:\n\n• Fading or discoloration from sun exposure\n• White, chalky residue caused by oxidation\n• Stains, water spots, or corrosion marks\n• Loss of shine compared to their original finish\n\nIf you notice any of these issues, restoration can bring your frames back to life without the cost of replacement—protecting your investment and refreshing the look of your home."
